(define/contract (count num1 num2 min_sum max_sum)
  (-> string? string? exact-integer? exact-integer? exact-integer?)
  
  (define mod 1000000007)
  
  (define (sum-digits n)
    (if (zero? n)
        0
        (+ (modulo n 10) (sum-digits (quotient n 10)))))
  
  (define (valid-sum? n)
    (let ((sum (sum-digits n)))
      (and (>= sum min_sum) (<= sum max_sum))))
  
  (define (iterate n1 n2)
    (if (> n1 n2)
        0
        (let ((next (iterate (+ n1 1) n2)))
          (if (valid-sum? n1)
              (modulo (+ 1 next) mod)
              next))))
  
  (let* ((start (string->number num1))
         (end (string->number num2))
         (result (iterate start end)))
    result))
